{"tid":1720392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 大學是據點 開花需持續","createTime":"2019-11-14T10:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:28:42.000Z","uid":17991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5461475c563c6523d3b7764fd8435759f95597","tid":1720392,"uid":17991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:39:29.000Z","msg":"當日暴大大戰，其他區圍魏救趙，結果不奏效，所以全城入暴大支持，而呢幾日狗冷處理，相反其他區捱打捱很超辛苦同埋今朝開花不太成功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要正視聽既係，保護大學由學生保護，入面有Hall 地型理解比其他人優勝，而暴大更不同於其他大學，地點較偏，不宜快速向外界支援，如果校外人在內苦等，不是等於浪費體力、資源嗎？<br />\n<br />\n當然我唔係話無需要入大學支援，而是外區人無必要長期留守，否則會令開花戰線不利。"},{"pid":"2b4be44eed3ee2aa035b431f304a4d355dc3eb04","tid":1720392,"uid":17991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cbdc0f4e1adee302ab98e16d077409c45c7764","tid":1720392,"uid":106627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"其實lingu隔離就係屯門公路同元朗公路<br />\n平時都好多車行<br />\n亦有天橋制高點<br />\nlingu/屯門手足們可以諗諗"},{"pid":"8987a2f125cbac473197019181dca6a2589c08de","tid":1720392,"uid":17991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4676991fb6c4b9e579250679f9a136213fd87770","tid":1720392,"uid":235645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"今晚到poly"},{"pid":"a8992b836ef5231fc8fbad2a87c2059bfedf8420","tid":1720392,"uid":17991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde405bfd67889e7a6a500c46e9409eceac8a1b0","tid":1720392,"uid":236087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"}]}